OL,3,CDepression and anxiety sufferers 'to
OL,4,Close sickness benefits in welfare
OL,5,Creforms'
OL,7,FPeople suffering with depression or
OL,8,Fanxiety will lose access to sickness
OL,9,Fbenefits as part of the Government's
OL,10,Fmajor welfare reforms, according to
OL,11,Freports.
OL,13,FMinisters will propose stopping
OL,14,Fregular payments for a range of mental
OL,15,Fhealth problems and instead argue for
OL,16,F"meaningful support" such as talking
OL,17,Ftherapy and social care packages, The
OL,18,FTimes reported.
