OL,3,CDepression and anxiety sufferers 'to
OL,4,Close sickness benefits in welfare
OL,5,Creforms'
OL,7,FWork and Pensions Secretary Mel Stride
OL,8,Fis expected to publish a green paper
OL,9,Fon Monday centring on personal
OL,10,Findependence payments (PIP) ` the main
OL,11,Fdisability benefit.
OL,13,FPrime Minister Rishi Sunak announced
OL,14,Fmajor changes to the welfare system
OL,15,Fearlier this month, when he said
OL,16,F"people with less severe mental health
OL,17,Fconditions should be expected to
OL,18,Fengage with the world of work".
