OL,3,CDepression and anxiety sufferers 'to
OL,4,Close sickness benefits in welfare
OL,5,Creforms'
OL,7,FSpeaking to The Times, Mr Stride said
OL,8,Fthe system should not be paying people
OL,9,Fto deal with the "ordinary
OL,10,Fdifficulties of life" and suggested
OL,11,Fthat many voters "deep down" agreed
OL,12,Fwith him.
