OL,5,Creforms'
OL,7,FMr Stride said a "whole plethora of
OL,8,Fthings", such as talking therapies,
OL,9,Fsocial care packages and respite care,
OL,10,Fcould be used as alternatives to
OL,11,Fbenefit payments.
OL,13,FHe added the main reason for the
OL,14,Fchanges was to provide better help and
OL,15,Fnot cut costs, but he acknowledged the
OL,16,Fcost "has to be one of the
OL,17,Fconsiderations".
OL,19,FThere are thought to be around 360,000
OL,20,Fpeople claiming PIP for anxiety and
OL,21,Fdepression, The Times reported.
